											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="A rasp of steel, and Jaheira stops short with a wet gasp - then falls forward, revealing Minsc holding his bloodied sword. The mind-meld dissipates, and he looks at her body with growing horror. Then to us, rage and grief building." />
